There are other positive emotions, but these are the seven most
powerful, and the ones most commonly used in creative effort. Master
these seven emotions (they can be mastered only by USE), and the other
positive emotions will be at your command when you need them. Remember,
in this connection, that you are studying a book which is intended to
help you develop a "money consciousness" by *filling your mind with
positive emotions*. One does not become money conscious by filling one's
mind with negative emotions.

THE SEVEN MAJOR NEGATIVE EMOTIONS  
(To be avoided)

